{"arkId":"cl010113545","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113545","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"Cafeti\u00e8re du service Demidoff","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cafeti\u00e8re du service Demidoff"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Restauration (1814-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1817","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 560 - Claude Ott, Acc\u00e8s r\u00e9serv\u00e9","room":"Salle 560, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1817,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Odiot, Jean-Baptiste-Claude","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"08\/06\/1763","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"23\/05\/1850","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3176320"},{"label":"Cavelier, Adrien-Louis-Marie","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12167","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; cafeti\u00e8re","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le pied, bord\u00e9 d\u2019une frise de laurier, est en forme de cloche. Le culot de la cafeti\u00e8re est grav\u00e9 de feuilles d\u2019eau. La panse est coup\u00e9e par un bandeau amati, \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de griffons de part et d\u2019autre d\u2019un masque de Mercure ail\u00e9 ; au-dessus est grav\u00e9e une frise de feuilles. Le bec \u00e0 base de feuilles d\u2019eau a son embouchure en t\u00eate de lionne. L\u2019anse est en nacre rivet\u00e9e et en argent dor\u00e9 ; elle s\u2019attache en bas par une t\u00eate d\u2019homme barbu et en haut, au bord du couvercle, par des feuilles d\u2019acanthe et d\u2019eau. La graine est en grenade. \r\nLa cafeti\u00e8re ne porte pas d\u2019armoiries.\r\n\r\nLe 15 f\u00e9vrier 1817, Odiot fournit au comte Nicolas Demidoff (1773-1828) un service \u00e0 th\u00e9 en vermeil \u00e0 manches de nacre, comme l\u0027attestent les archives de la maison Odiot.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Fabricant (J.B.C.O., un soufflet de forge) (au revers et \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle)\r ; Moyenne garantie (au bord du pied)\r ; Paris, argent, 1809-1819, 1er titre  (sur le col)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Profondeur","value":"9","displayDimension":"9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"21,7","displayDimension":"21,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"16","displayDimension":"16 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9\r\nMat\u00e9riau : nacre","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Nicolas Demidoff (1774-1828) ; son fils, Anatole Demidoff (1812-1870) ; probablement vendu \u00e0 la maison Hancock en 1863, et achet\u00e9 par Joseph-Xavier-Alfred de Morton, comte de La Chapelle (1830-1914) ; vendu en 1914 \u00e0 un \u00ab gentleman \u00bb anglais ; ensemble dispers\u00e9 \u00e0 la vente \u00e0 New York, American Art Association, Anderson Galleries, 15 d\u00e9cembre 1928 ; legs de Mme Audrey B. Love, par